-- MOVES-Credit Suisse names Barclays exec to leveraged finance unit
-- 
-- Thu Jul 31, 2014 01:40PM EDT
-- None



July 31 (Reuters) - Credit Suisse Group AG <CSGN.VX> named Matthew Grinnell as a managing director in the leveraged finance and sponsors group.

Grinnell, who joins from Barclays <BARC.L>, will be responsible for Credit Suisse's private equity relationships.